            "text":"The station reactor section holds the HDG Reactors.  The reactors convert High-energy Density Gluon fuel into useful power for the station.  Without at least one working reactor, nothing else on the station can function.  When you start to expand the station, you will need more reactors ( or better ones) to meet the energy requirements of the station.  Our station reactor section has sustained damage, and so has the reactor itself.  We are only producing half of our potential output.  Be sure to repair this as soon as possible.",
